Interface IAtomicSwComponentType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, ISwComponentType
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface IAtomicSwComponentType
extends IEntity, ISwComponentType
    IAtomicSwComponentType: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    An atomic software component is atomic in the sense that it cannot be further decomposed and distributed across multiple ECUs.
